{"type":"message","id":"89aed6c3","parentId":"50ee73d6","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:14:00.198Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01Ru4p1EXHoGYWxTkGAZKiHF","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FullName                                                                                             LastWriteTime     \r\n--------                                                                                             -------------     \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs                                  25/03/2026 21:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\README.md                             25/03/2026 14:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\KnowledgeBase                    25/03/2026 19:0...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\00_CONTEXT.md                    25/03/2026 14:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\01_FRAMEWORK_RESEARCH.md         25/03/2026 14:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\02_GPT_BRAINSTORM_ANALYSIS.md    25/03/2026 14:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\03_PIPELINE_MAP.md               25/03/2026 14:2...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\04_BRANCH_ARCHITECTURE.md        25/03/2026 15:0...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\05_MULTI_MACHINE_ARCHITECTURE.md 25/03/2026 16:3...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\06_MODEL_STRATEGY.md             25/03/2026 18:0...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\07_BRAINDUMP_OPENCLAW.md         25/03/2026 21:1...\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\KnowledgeBase\\AlexFinn    